There was one other sighting in Sun City West on or around October 9th 2012
divs: Sighting DetailsAt my residence back open to sky patio slab.At about 7:30pm,I notice a large number of jets going back and forth overhead in a constant jet roar for about 15 minutes and then they all gone.Almost immediately afterwards I see a Jupiter sized light in the southwest headed north east flying towards me then on a straight track away.I sight with 10x zeiss binoculars..no frame just round light moving at average aircraft speed.Light flickered then disapear in a .quite clear sky at about in Casseopia.This was Oct. 9 2012.Yesterday Oct.8 at 7:00pm saw same thing except moving slower speed and no jets prior.
Summary: jupiter sized regular aircraft speed no frame then disappeared
